select B.sfrstcr_pidm Student_pidm, SUBSTR(SUBSTR(H.SPRIDEN_ID,1,2)||CAST(ORA_HASH(H.SPRIDEN_ID,999999) AS VARCHAR2(60))||'000000',1,8) Student_ID, C.scbcrse_title, E.STVTERM_DESC, D.SSBSECT_term_code, D.ssbsect_crn, C.SCBCRSE_CRSE_NUMB, C.SCBCRSE_SUBJ_CODE, A.SSRMEET_BEGIN_TIME, A.SSRMEET_END_TIME, A.SSRMEET_BLDG_CODE, A.SSRMEET_ROOM_CODE, A.SSRMEET_CREDIT_HR_SESS, (A.SSRMEET_MON_DAY || '-' ||A.SSRMEET_TUE_DAY|| '-' ||A.SSRMEET_WED_DAY|| '-' ||A.SSRMEET_THU_DAY|| '-' ||A.SSRMEET_FRI_DAY) as Schedule
, NVL ( SUBSTR(SUBSTR(G.SPRIDEN_ID,1,2)||CAST(ORA_HASH(G.SPRIDEN_ID,999999) AS VARCHAR2(60))||'000000',1,8), ' ') inst_id,
DECODE (G.spriden_id, NULL, NULL, LOWER ( SUBSTR(SUBSTR(G.SPRIDEN_ID,1,2)||CAST(ORA_HASH(G.SPRIDEN_ID,999999) AS VARCHAR2(60))||'000000',1,8)) || '@creighton.edu') inst_email, REPLACE ( NVL ( SUBSTR(G.SPRIDEN_LAST_NAME,1,1)||CAST(ORA_HASH(G.SPRIDEN_LAST_NAME) AS VARCHAR2(60)), 'TBD') || ', ' || SUBSTR(G.SPRIDEN_FIRST_NAME,1,1)||CAST(ORA_HASH(G.SPRIDEN_FIRST_NAME) AS VARCHAR2(60))
|| ' ' || G.spriden_mi, 'TBD,', 'TBD') instructor, NVL ( SUBSTR(G.SPRIDEN_LAST_NAME,1,1)||CAST(ORA_HASH(G.SPRIDEN_LAST_NAME) AS VARCHAR2(60)), 'TBD') inst_last_name, SUBSTR(G.SPRIDEN_FIRST_NAME,1,1)||CAST(ORA_HASH(G.SPRIDEN_FIRST_NAME) AS VARCHAR2(60)) inst_first_name, G.spriden_mi inst_middle_name from saturn.SSRMEET A, Saturn.SFRSTCR B, Saturn.SCBCRSE C, saturn.SSBSECT D, saturn.stvterm E, saturn.sirasgn F, saturn.spriden G ,saturn.spriden H where B.sfrstcr_pidm = H.SPRIDEN_PIDM AND H.SPRIDEN_CHANGE_IND(+) is null and A.ssrmeet_term_code='201670' And A.ssrmeet_term_code=B.sfrstcr_term_code and A.ssrmeet_term_code =E.STVTERM_CODE and a.ssrmeet_mtyp_code <> 'EXAM' and A.SSRMEET_SCHD_CODE='L' and D.ssbsect_crn=B.SFRSTCR_CRN and A.SSRMEET_CRN=B.SFRSTCR_CRN and D.SSBSECT_term_code=B.sfrstcr_term_code and D.ssbsect_crn = B.SFRSTCR_CRN and C.SCBCRSE_CRSE_NUMB =D.SSBSECT_CRSE_NUMB and C.SCBCRSE_SUBJ_CODE = D.SSBSECT_SUBJ_CODE and C.SCBCRSE_EFF_TERM = (SELECT MAX (b.scbcrse_eff_term) FROM saturn.scbcrse b WHERE b.scbcrse_subj_code = D.ssbsect_subj_code AND b.scbcrse_crse_numb = D.ssbsect_crse_numb AND b.scbcrse_eff_term <= D.ssbsect_term_code) And F.sirasgn_term_code(+) = A.ssrmeet_term_code AND F.sirasgn_crn(+) = A.ssrmeet_crn AND F.sirasgn_category(+) = A.ssrmeet_catagory and F.sirasgn_primary_ind ='Y' And G.spriden_pidm(+)=F.sirasgn_pidm and G.spriden_change_ind(+) is nUll
